text: Never Gonna Not Dance Again is a pop song by American singer Pink, released on November 4, 2022. It is from her ninth upcoming studio album, Trustfall. Critics have described this song as "vibrant, joyful, and euphoric" and "an upbeat anthem about dancing through our perpetually hard times". It commercially reached the top 10 in 7 countries. ==References== Category:Pop songs Category:2022 songs Category:Pink (singer) songs
